_sText:
Finally the map lots of peoples been waiting for... I give you: Phy_doomed.
Please do not judge the map by the images. It's a VERY good map and will make you play CS Source longer than ever!

Map contains about this:

Exploding car

An extremely  fun to play with torpedo

Lock down for T

Over 4 secrets

Custom model

Custom textures

Custom sound

All in the .bsp!


Do not say its flat and ugly before playing it. I've heard enough of the dorks saying "ugly. flat. no I will not test it." This map is impossible to take screenshots of and show the extreme fun in it. And if you don't believe me I got a whole army of CSS nerds that loves this map.

Displacements -> Yes I had it once. Totally killed the fun. Removed.


Thanks! 

/Freelancer
